Rose
's
bosom
He could not have judged better;
the woodbine was an emblem of her
sweetness
, the
myrtle of her love and
constancy
.
Farewel,
blest
pair! may your portion of life be
pure, and unmixed with gall; may your
happiness
be as permanent as your innocence and truth are
conspicuous
.
The RESCUE.
I head
been at the play.
A young creature, in the box adjoining that I
