.
I have frequently been engaged in
disputes
concerning
women of this
profession
it puts me
beyond
all patience to hear people advance an opinion
so
very contracted and illiberal, as that of
supposing
no woman can be virtuous who is on the
stage
I
know many at this time who are ornaments not
only
