,
will find opportunities of doing evil.It is a
great pity
so
many women belonging to the
stage
are
thus inclined; but why
should
we, on account of
those
that are bad, condemn a Siddons, Brunton,
Kemble, or Pope?Why
should
a woman, if
she
is a good wife, daughter, or mother, be
less
