But all
these
precautions were vain. During my
absence
, one of the
servants
had entered the room,
which in my agitated
state
of mind I had forgot to
lock, and
instantly
alarmed her
mistress
. At my
return I found my poor Maria in an agony of grief,
which, however, was happily of no ill
consequence
to
