when the old incumbent died I
should
have the
living; but I was
mistaken
. In a few months the
old man paid the debt of nature, and the living was
disposed
of to another
person
.
Our
disappointment
was very greatbut the two
hundred pounds Maria
possessed
hindered us from
being immediately
exposed
to want, but that
