you for your
salary's
being
stopped
Pray how have you lived
since
your return to
England
?
But poorly my Lord; I have but thirty pounds a
year.
My Lord again looked up; but it was a look of
disbelief
.
And how many children have you?
Two, my Lord; a boy and a girl.
Well, I will
see
and do
something
for the boy
and let me thinkyes, there's the living at
Wiltham
,
about three hundred a yearthat will
just
suit
youcall on me again in a day or two; I
shall
always
be glad to
see
you.
So
