mean-looking people.
Mr Bauble waits below,
said
the
servant
.
Desire
Mr. Bauble to walk upand when
Miss
L'
Estrange
comes, let me know.
The jeweller entered, and in a few moments after,
Miss
L'
Estrange
;
whose
levity of carriage,
studied
