I repaired immediately to his
Lordship
's
house
inquired for the lady, but was denied admittancea
chariot and four was at the doorI feared
some
soul
play; and thinking there was no time to be
lost
, I
watched my opportunity, and, putting on my ring,
went into the
house
, and up to the Lady's apartment.
I found her
sitting
on a
sopha
with a large quantity
of jewels, &c. on a table before her; the was
busied
in
packing them up, but often turned and
addressed
some
