.
Mr. Selby became acquainted with the lovely
friends before Emily had attained her eighteenth
yearher
sense
and penetration charmed him; and
her
person
, having then all the attractions of
blooming
youth, he declared
himself
her loverhe
frequently
laughed and romped with
Lassonia
, but
never
