your
happiness
; indeed I did not know, or I never
would have
visited
my happy rivalI never thought
your love was divided, and the certainty of it came
so
sudden
upon my heart, that weak and
unprepared
as it was, it could not bear the
shock
take
care of my children,
said
she
, adieu my love; my
heart may break, but my tongue will never
reproach
you.
Her
