When fifteen years old, he was apprenticed to a
capital Cabinet-maker; a very
handsome
premium
was given with him; but he was too much of the
gentleman to attend to
business
, and when he came
of age he
assumed
the
dress
and manners of a man
of
fashion
;
expensive
