, which they have no
laudable
method to obtain, has hurried
thousands
into
actions which imbitter the
last
hours of life with
poverty,
shame
, and
remorse
.
As I
finished
these
remarks, I looked up,
expecting
an
answer
from my companion; but
whether
my
